race.comment: IN OUR HEARTS (10) has progressed the right way this prep and looks ready to peak after going down by just a long neck at Naracoorte. Carries no weight again and maps for a soft run. Very hard to beat. LEGAL DRAMA (5) has been sound in both runs back without threatening but should be nearing her top third-up. Draws well and has the platform to play a major role. ENNISCRONE (2) hasn't fired yet in his debut prep but has been freshened 32 days and changed environments. Trialled well in between, though he'll need a clever ride from the wide draw. Capable of improving. FRENCH REIGN (3) showed signs of life last time out when finishing midfield. Is open to further improvement fourth-up and is worth some thought.
